data.description: Welcome to this adorable 3 bed/2 bath ranch situated on a gorgeous 1.38-acre lot in the desirable Green School District! As you enter, you will immediately notice the open floor plan. The newly carpeted living room leads to the dining room. The fully appliance kitchen offers ample counterspace and plenty of cabinetry for storage. There is a large owner's suite, 2 more nicely sized bedrooms and an additional full bath. The laundry room is located on the first floor for one floor living at its finest. The unfinished basement has been framed/studded making it easy to finish a great lower-level rec room! Home has many updates 2023 A/C and furnace blower motor, 2023 water softener and osmosis, 2023 patio, firepit and steps. Plus, much much more!!! Don't forget about the Outbuilding that offers an additional car garage space with lots of additional storage. Don't miss out on this rare find! Call to schedule a showing today!
